<div class="jumbotron jumbotron-fluid">
    <div class="container">
        {{!-- <img class="img" src="images/coffee.png" class="rounded float-right" alt="..."> --}}
        <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to Coffee Time Trivia!</h1>
        <hr class="my-4"> {{#if isUser}}
        <p>Howdy, {{user.username}}!</p>
        <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="/game" role="button">Play Trivia</a>
        <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="/dashboard" role="button">Dashboard</a>
        <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="/logout" role="button">Logout</a>
        {{/if}} {{#unless isUser}}
        <p>You are not currently signed in.</p>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg drkbtn" id="modalBtn">Sign Up / Sign In</button>
        {{/unless}}
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
    <h1 class="display-4">About this App</h1>
    <p>
        Welcome to Coffee Time Trivia. A trivia game where you can add your own questions about anything and everything. You can
        start answering trivia questions right away. Just login grab a cup of your favorite Joe and start answering. Once
        you have started the questions will come at you randomly, so you do not have to worry about them coming in the same
        order every time you play. The system will remember your answers and try to match you with new and challenging questions
        every time.</p>
    <p>
        If you decide that you want to contribute to our community, you can always add your own questions to the catalog for other
        Coffee Time Trivia players. Just simply submit your question(s) and answer(s) to the site, they will automatically
        be approved and added to the queue of questions. All players then get the opportunity to vote on your submitted questions.
        You will not be asked to answer your own question nor can you vote on your submitted question(s). You will be asked
        and allowed to vote on questions that others have posted. As long as people up-vote your question it stays in the
        game for all users to enjoy. As soon as your question gets enough downvotes to override any up-votes, it is removed
        from the trivia question list. Have fun and enjoy your Coffee trivia break!
    </p>
</div>

<div class="modal fade" id="login-modal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="results-modal" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                    <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                </button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <form>
                            <h4>Sign Up</h4>
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label for="usernameCreate">Username</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="usernameCreate" placeholder="Enter username">
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label for="passwordCreate">Password</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="passwordCreate" placeholder="Enter password">
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="passwordCheck" placeholder="Reenter password">
                            </div>
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" id="createSubmit">Submit</button>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <form>
                            <h4>Sign In</h4>
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label for="usernameInput">Username</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="usernameInput" placeholder="Enter username">
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label for="passwordInput">Password</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="passwordInput" placeholder="Enter password">
                            </div>
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" id="loginSubmit">Submit</button>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script src="js/account.js"></script>